description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 432, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50548-43532-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [432 Votes, Hall of Fame]
